        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No PFAS in Cosmetics Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to issue and finalize a rule to ban the use of intentionally added perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substances in cosmetics. </p>]]>
        </text>
